  <span id="freeText2758681654008680096" style="display:none">Jeanette Miller crafts a romantic plot full of twists and turns that lead to a heart fluttering conclusion. <br /><br />Ashlyn Carter feels betrayed, disappointment, and angry at the way her life has spiraled off the happily ever after path. Moving back to her home town with her three year old and a heart breaking secret, she hopes for a fresh start. Enter a couple of eligible suitors, her boy crazy sister, and a fixer-upper house and what happens is a health dose of reality that awakens Ashlyn to find her decisions alone determine her happiness. Will she realize she can still live a happily ever after?</span>
