        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1233768889" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1467475580719060481">This was basically a good story that kept me reading clear into the early morning hours. My only beef was that there was a lot of repeating of thoughts...one might say...a repetitious and redundant replay of repeating thoughts over and over...:0) as Ashlyn processed her feelings. However, it was otherwise well written. I would read other books by Jeanette Miller.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


