        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1323976538" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13586960571028443568">I would give this book 4.5 stars. It wasn&apos;t my favorite, but it was still a very good read. I think that the plot was well thought out and I liked how much Ashlyn changed throughout the book. I loved the character that the author gave Katie, I think it added a lot to the book. The book, in my opinion, wasn&apos;t super exciting but it did have some heartwarming moments.</span>
  <span id="freeText13586960571028443568" style="display:none">I would give this book 4.5 stars. It wasn't my favorite, but it was still a very good read. I think that the plot was well thought out and I liked how much Ashlyn changed throughout the book. I loved the character that the author gave Katie, I think it added a lot to the book. The book, in my opinion, wasn't super exciting but it did have some heartwarming moments.</span>
